    {
      "_id": "y0G6Hcirsc4uakIL",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp",
      "name": "Shake It Off",
      "sort": 800000,
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The tarnworm would be affected by a condition or adverse effect (such as <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.dN8QBNuTiaBHCKUe]{Baleful Polymorph}</em>)</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The tarnworm negates the triggering condition or effect. Effects from artifacts, deities, or a similarly powerful source can't be avoided in this way.</p>"
