    {
      "_id": "53LkbbyoyISSppMe",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
      "name": "Tarnworm Venom",
      "sort": 1000000,
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:32]</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> [[/r {5d6}[poison]]]{5d6 poison damage} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 2} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> [[/r {6d6}[poison]]]{6d6 poison damage}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 2} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> [[/r {8d6}[poison]]]{8d6 poison damage} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 2} (1 round)</p>"
